OL,3,CONS staff to vote on strikes in
OL,4,Cdispute over working from home
OL,6,F(ONS) staff are being balloted for in
OL,7,Fa dispute over working from home.
OL,9,FAround 1,000 members of the Public and
OL,10,FCommercial Services union (PCS) based
OL,11,Fin several offices, including in
OL,12,FEdinburgh, London, Manchester and
OL,13,FDarlington, will vote in the coming
OL,14,Fweeks on whether to launch a campaign
OL,15,Fof industrial action.
OL,17,FThe union said its members were being
OL,18,Ftold to work from their office for two
OL,19,Fdays a week, after previously being
OL,20,Fallowed to work from home since the
OL,21,Fstart of the lockdown.
