OL,3,CONS staff to vote on strikes in
OL,4,Cdispute over working from home
OL,6,FPCS officials said many staff work
OL,7,Ffrom their office several days a week
OL,8,Fanyway, with others accepting jobs at
OL,9,Fthe ONS because they were promised the
OL,10,Fflexibility to work from home.
OL,12,FPCS general secretary Fran Heathcote
OL,13,Fsaid: "Post-pandemic arrangements at
OL,14,FONS have been an example of best
OL,15,Fpractice in flexible and sustainable
OL,16,Fways of working, so it's a mystery why
OL,17,Fmanagers have changed their minds,
OL,18,Fespecially after having regularly
OL,19,Freassured members they could remain
OL,20,Fworking more flexibly.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/4
