OL,4,Cdispute over working from home
OL,6,F"No evidence-based business case has
OL,7,Fbeen made for their rushed decision -
OL,8,Fa move that has caused anger among
OL,9,Fstaff demoralised by the lack of trust
OL,10,Fand the need for rapid changes to
OL,11,Ftheir childcare and other
OL,12,Farrangements."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the ONS said: "The
OL,15,FONS has had a hybrid working model for
OL,16,Fsome years now, in line with the wider
OL,17,FCivil Service.
