OL,6,F"Face-to-face interaction supports
OL,7,Fcollaboration and fosters learning and
OL,8,Finnovation, while some tasks can be
OL,9,Fdone as effectively or even more
OL,10,Feffectively at home.
OL,12,F"We are applying this flexibly to help
OL,13,Fbalance business and personal needs,
OL,14,Fand have offered all colleagues
OL,15,Fextensive support."
